  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't know him at that time, yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But from the others who were there, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It were four, five sisters and two brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- well, I was 30-- at '33, how old was I?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was 36.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we will maybe come to that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I found out from people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because otherwise, you know--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- when he--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know he left the house that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, two days later, came already the German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was one, two, three.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they throw me out from this apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to my mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And later, my brother is an engineer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a tour-- they-- they already-- this-- put which place will be the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was assigned from a-- a-- a factory or what, to build a hospital, to remodel for a hospital.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had a little push.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we got a-- a-- a room in the ghetto, which considered a good.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because considered he an engineer, I am a doctor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was a gas range and running water.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was-- Park Avenue, Fifth Avenue is nothing in comparison with this, what we got, running water and gas range.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When did they establish the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Immediately?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but we had to move in the beginning of January of 1940, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The slums, the worst, which there was no sewer-- [? sewering ?] thing in it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was no sanitary facilities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And no apartment.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew that they-- they-- the Jewish-- what do you say?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], how, what do you say?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish law said we-- the-- the Jews, we knew, have to move by that-and-that day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
